Installation of e3 on AIX 3.1

0 su
1 mv e3 /usr/bin; mv et /usr/bin
2 mv e.ex /usr/etc
3 mv ehelp.hlp /usr/etc
4 edit /etc/profile
5 add epath=/usr/etc;export epath
6 individual users may set up an alias e=/usr/bin/e3
7 if you open up a tn larger than 80x25 export LINES=?? and COLUMNS=?? and
  e3 will fill the window.  This is done for you if you use aixterm.
